  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/1b5226624d57b1737875d8fedcb4b825.avif?t=1635005917\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>This package includes <strong>DEAD DOZEN Escape</strong> and <strong>DEAD DOZEN</strong>:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1) DEAD DOZEN ESCAPE</h2><i>Single-player, co-op</i><br><br>Form a team with up to 4 players and escape from the depths of the mysterious pyramid in the heart of Siberia, or do it all on your own. Various challenges and hordes of AI-controlled ghouls await you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2) DEAD DOZEN</h2><i>Online PvP (up to 12 players)</i><br><br>A competitive PvP game where you turn into a ghoul after your death as a human. Loot, barricade and cooperate when you play as a Survivor or infiltrate, infect and eat your former human friends when you play as a Ghoul.<br><br><strong>DIE AS A SURVIVOR, RISE AS A GHOUL</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.poster.avif?t=1635005917\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.webm?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.mp4?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get up instantly after death and kill your former friends.<br><br><strong>DESTRUCTIBLE ENVIRONMENT</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/ac95f5e4e973a3b7df60965562e27e51.poster.avif?t=1635005917\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/ac95f5e4e973a3b7df60965562e27e51.webm?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/ac95f5e4e973a3b7df60965562e27e51.mp4?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Destroy brittle walls, breach ceilings and floors.<br><br><strong>GET THE BEST FROM BEING A GHOUL</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/c1d550e51632fcd417cf1ce3fcfc0b7a.poster.avif?t=1635005917\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/c1d550e51632fcd417cf1ce3fcfc0b7a.webm?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/c1d550e51632fcd417cf1ce3fcfc0b7a.mp4?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Use your special abilities and infect survivors to spread the panic among them.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/1b5226624d57b1737875d8fedcb4b825.avif?t=1635005917\" width=616 height=200 /></span><br><br>This package includes <strong>DEAD DOZEN Escape</strong> and <strong>DEAD DOZEN</strong>:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1) DEAD DOZEN ESCAPE</h2><i>Single-player, co-op</i><br><br>Form a team with up to 4 players and escape from the depths of the mysterious pyramid in the heart of Siberia, or do it all on your own. Various challenges and hordes of AI-controlled ghouls await you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2) DEAD DOZEN</h2><i>Online PvP (up to 12 players)</i><br><br>A competitive PvP game where you turn into a ghoul after your death as a human. Loot, barricade and cooperate when you play as a Survivor or infiltrate, infect and eat your former human friends when you play as a Ghoul.<br><br><strong>DIE AS A SURVIVOR, RISE AS A GHOUL</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.poster.avif?t=1635005917\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.webm?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/d0e9bb56e64f367255f2e327a02012b2.mp4?t=1635005917\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get up instantly after death and kill your former friends.<br><br><strong>DESTRUCTIBLE ENVIRONMENT</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/749780/extras/ac95f5e4e973a3b7df60965562e27e51.poster.avif?t=1635005917\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared